        <li>Is spam, advertising, or promotional material not authorized by us</li>
      </ul>
    `,
  },
  {
    id: 'use',
    title: 'Acceptable Use',
    content: `
      <p>You agree not to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Use the Service for any unlawful purpose</li>
