        <li>Create derivative works based on the content</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Certificates earned through the Service may be shared on professional networks and with employers to verify your accomplishments.</p>
    `,
  },
  {
    id: 'termination',
    title: 'Termination',
    content: `
      <p>We may terminate or suspend your account immediately, without prior notice or liability, for any reason, including without limitation if you breach the Terms.</p>
      <p>Upon termination:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your right to use the Service will immediately cease</li>
